Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:10.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:39.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A new dungeon was discovered on \Nthe border of the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:45.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, Noelle, and Luck of the Black \NBulls were assigned to investigate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:47.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:53.49,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:54.65,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:57.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:00:58.06,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:06.23,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The dungeon was filled with traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:10.42,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:12.13,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:15.59,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to die if we stay with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:18.26,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:21.51,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm about to reach my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:25.52,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:28.06,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,There are others here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:31.27,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest looking one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.86,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Something important just came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:39.37,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm leaving the dungeon \Nexploration to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:47.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of traps might spring up,\NI'll slice through them with my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:51.84,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We're alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:57.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:00.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A trap! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:05.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:11.36,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Noelle were in danger. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:13.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:27.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Such precise and powerful magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.54,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.51,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:36.09,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I've repaid my debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:37.80,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:59.91,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:04.11,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:08.87,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:13.17,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.27,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.47,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:16.34,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.92,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.92,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:28.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:31.14,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:34.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:40.15,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:46.28,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.45,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:53.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.84,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:00.92,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:08.56,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Diamond Mage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.22,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Vangeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.54,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:35.00,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, about the exploration \Nof the new dungeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:39.86,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you send that new peasant \Nrecruit on such an important mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.65,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Do you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:44.84,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:50.60,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,I, Alecdora Sandler, am ready to die for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:56.10,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'd like you to trust \Nhim, too. Because I trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:05:00.61,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,He's also a member of the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:04.69,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll become an even \Nmore powerful force for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:05.61,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:13.24,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... We need him to get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:22.05,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So he's Yuno? And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.88,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:28.39,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,why did you bother saving them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:32.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Our only mission is to explore this dungeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:36.63,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, to quickly reach the \Ntreasure chamber buried deep below.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.12,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any time \Nto waste on these fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:44.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuno. What's the deal \Nwith this rude four-eyed dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's my senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.36,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Four—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.09,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're the rude one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:52.87,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a four... er, I'm a nobleman! \NHow dare you address me so casually?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.66,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's flustered all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:58.69,sign_8504_83_Member_of_the_Go,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}Member of the Golden Dawn\N{\fs30}Mimosa Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.69,top,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Good day, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:05.24,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I've seen you since \Nthe royal banquet last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.35,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Noelle's cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.39,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.96,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It just had to be her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:22.42,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard the Black Bulls are a very \Nbarbaric squad. Have you been faring well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.26,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And are you doing okay, Mimosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.07,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:31.66,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure someone as dense as you \Ncan make it in the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:35.48,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Everyone is so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:39.29,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I've been able to \Nuse my magic without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:46.26,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, you weren't \Nable to control your magic at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.92,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Have things improved since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:52.90,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,She's as obliviously rude as ever. \NShe still pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.43,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've been working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:07:00.85,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the three of us recently received \Na star from the Wizard King himself
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.94,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,for another mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.73,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:10.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We just got a star, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:11.84,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:12.70,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:19.33,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Newbies from the Black Bulls wouldn't \Nbe awarded stars so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:25.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We {\i1}did{\i0} get one!\NWe're at minus thirty now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:30.05,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's laughable that you've been \Ncharged with this mission, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:33.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King appointed \Nus to this mission himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:35.01,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Such a blatant lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.30,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.14,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He really is flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:44.74,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I heard \Nthere'd be three of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.98,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:50.94,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me they left you two and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:55.70,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Or did they fall prey to one of the traps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:59.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't run away, nor did he \Nfall prey to any of the traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.93,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Then where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.96,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.31,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can tell them he \Nditched us and went off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.97,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:18.81,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, it's clear your lot consists \Nof filth that leaves new recruits behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.85,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls... How unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.06,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're an embarrassment to the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:30.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to conquer this \Ndungeon first for the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:34.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Gol... No, Goober?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:38.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No, uh... you guys with the \Nweird masked captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.87,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Goober? It's Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:44.87,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,And "weird mask"? You scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:49.55,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You dare mock our esteemed \NCaptain Vangeance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.28,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones with a weird captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:55.18,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of freak runs around with all \Nthose muscles bulging out of a tank top?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:59.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!\NHe's manly and totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:04.00,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you talk to a noble like that?!\NNot to mention your senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:07.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me! My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:08.15,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.74,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's really flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.81,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:18.77,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to show you the difference \Nbetween the top of the Magic Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.82,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,and the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:21.70,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.98,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:28.65,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Plant Creation Magic: Magic Flower Guidepost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:41.85,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Ah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:45.77,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned the basic layout of the dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:47.60,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.60,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He can carry all three of them so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.66,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:07.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive as always, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:10.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:22.15,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see which of us gets to \Nthe treasure chamber first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:00.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of us can use tracking spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to check \Nevery path very carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:09.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid? Oh, right, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:12.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we'll get lost before \Nwe even find the treasure chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.43,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Take the next right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.64,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.01,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What was that fool's name? Asta? The nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.58,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:39.84,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him, anyway? I couldn't \Nsense any magic from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.34,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:46.81,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What was the captain \Nof the Black Bulls thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.00,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,taking someone like him—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.45,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:54.60,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's best that you don't underestimate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:59.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,They'll do well enough to get \Nout of this dungeon alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:05.12,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to conquer this dungeon as \Nfast as possible, for our country's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.49,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,I have a report for the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:16.13,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,The two Magic Knight Squads,\Nthe Golden Dawn and the Black Bulls,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.09,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,have begun their investigations \Nof the dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:23.34,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,We have also confirmed that a military mage \Nsquad from the Diamond Kingdom is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:28.21,main,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,Our neighbor, the Diamond Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:31.91,main,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,They've been trying to expand \Ntheir borders lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:40.55,sign_18011_185_Clover_Kingdom_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(926,1459)}Clover\NKingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:40.55,sign_18011_186_Dungeon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(926,1459)}Dungeon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:40.55,sign_18011_187_Diamond__Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(926,1459)}Diamond\NKingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.93,main,Man c,0000,0000,0000,,They're an aggressive kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:37.73,main,Man D,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be trouble if we let \Nthem steal the ancient magic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.53,main,Man D,0000,0000,0000,,that might be in the dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.95,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Who's in charge of this \Ninvasion from Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:48.95,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. The one leading the \Nenemy squad is Lotus of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.85,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:53.21,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I've met him on the battlefield before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:55.42,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:58.64,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The magic he used was really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:03.59,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, should you sound so amused right now?\NShouldn't you be more concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:08.98,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's fine. I hear Yami's \Nsent an interesting one on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:09.89,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:15.39,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus is strong, but our \Nkids are strong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.40,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.08,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You're so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.95,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:30.58,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:35.08,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing good comes of \Nraising hurdles too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.76,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Enthusiastic young power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.84,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Terrifying, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:45.42,sign_19657_205_Lotus_of_the_Aby,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus of the Abyss
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:44.14,top,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You took my subordinates out in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.42,top,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.21,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they are just subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:51.93,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're their boss and you're \Nstrong, there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:56.43,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,So you fight wrapped in \Nyour own lightning magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:01.62,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is that practical, \Nbut you seem pretty powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:03.07,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,And you're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.14,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You're making the most \Nof your youthful strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:08.95,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this old man shaking in his boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.16,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of magic do you fight with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.37,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You seem rather enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:22.58,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You Clover people are also after this \Ndungeon's treasure chamber, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:26.17,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.72,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:32.47,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm pretty sure \Nwe don't have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.27,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just compete nonviolently!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.73,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, great idea. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:38.73,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.81,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.02,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He dodged me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:45.86,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.53,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, that was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:54.63,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I can see why the citizens of \Nthe Clover Kingdom would be mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:59.32,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we've been trying \Nto invade here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:03.29,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for all the trouble the \NDiamond Kingdom's been causing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:08.47,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,But you see, our kingdom's running out \Nof resources, so we have it rough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.41,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,If we want to survive,\Nwe don't really have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.97,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Living can be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:18.35,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I have three daughters...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.60,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:30.03,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! I don't care as long \Nas I get to fight strong people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:34.78,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I've caught the \Neye of some real trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.26,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,This old man might just cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:49.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?\NThe gravity's all messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:52.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we're going the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.27,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's definitely {\i1}not{\i0} treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:11.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Stupidsta! That has to be a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:14.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:19.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's inside! \NI wonder what's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:23.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop! What are you \Ngoing to do if it's a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:33.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why did you have to \Nshow me that, Shrimpsta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my faul—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.44,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You're so full of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.73,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Stop dodging, and let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:51.48,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Please? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:00.99,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I remember. The Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:04.25,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought with your captain before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.58,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty hot-headed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.00,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,What? You know the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.61,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:16.01,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me this lovely scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:18.08,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I pissed my pants and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.51,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, that was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.52,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,He had a very unusual fighting style.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:28.02,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,He was the only younger opponent \NI've had that I couldn't defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.19,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That makes you even more worth figh—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:34.86,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.05,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.16,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.66,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It's... nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.93,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,So slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:52.58,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little, fall right into the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:59.43,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Magic? But I don't \Nremember getting hit by his magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:08.06,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You see, this whole room \Nis enveloped in my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:12.57,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Very thin smoke that you can't really see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:18.57,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Weakening Smoke Magic: Garden\Nof Plundering Smoke, if you were wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:21.70,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,My body's not listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:27.79,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,A spell that lowers physical \Nabilities? When did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:33.04,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling you'd block it \Nif it were a visible attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:37.61,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I lowered my magical \Nability as much as I could
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:39.88,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,so I could use this without you noticing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:45.30,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,While you were fighting my subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:51.32,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't go out in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:55.23,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,They sacrificed themselves \Nso I could use this spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:01.30,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,It's very important, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:02.49,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:15.50,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there. Once we\Nget through this tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:26.04,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,How amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:31.52,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to dungeons? \NThat wasn't very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how you get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.56,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the Black Bulls aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:42.99,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. There's no way they'd beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.49,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.75,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It ripped through her \Nmagic-shielding cloak...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:02.51,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,She's an expert at sensing mana,\Nbut she didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.07,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:09.88,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't a trap spell... \NWhat is this magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.44,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.94,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Who stands in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.01,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:28.26,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Friends you can trust are \Nworth their weight in gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:33.46,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but stay there a while and get weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:38.98,flashbackitalics,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Win...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:43.46,flashbackitalics,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Win...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:49.47,flashbackitalics,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Keep winning, Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:54.47,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.36,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.64,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,since things actually got interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.57,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,More... More!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.00,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:28.28,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not pluck a bud \Nthat's still so young...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:55.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:58.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:00.63,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:05.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:11.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:13.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:16.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:25.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:27.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:30.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:32.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:35.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:41.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:47.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:50.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:06.28,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.29,0:23:05.78,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:09.78,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}A Lotus Flower\NThat Doesn't Bloom\NIs Just a Lotus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:09.78,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,A Lotus Flower That Doesn't \NBloom Is Just a Lotus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:14.03,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I have three daughters...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:17.04,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,"When I get older,\NI'm going to marry you, Daddy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:21.04,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,And all three of them fight over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:23.84,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,But once they hit puberty...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:25.59,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,"Get away from me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:28.09,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't mix my laundry with yours!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:31.01,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:37.21,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,And my wife was so nice when \Nwe first met, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:36.34,top,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This is really annoying, so I think I'm \Nready to fall into the abyss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:42.53,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done yet. It's finally getting fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.53,0:23:44.32,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,More! Let's play more!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.32,0:23:47.25,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kill each other! Please, Mister?
